00:01:03,824 --> 00:01:05,034
Let us serve the meal.

7
00:01:05,117 --> 00:01:06,160
Yes, sure.

8
00:01:43,197 --> 00:01:44,573
It's Ms. Best Talent.

9
00:01:44,657 --> 00:01:46,158
It's been a while.

10
00:01:49,078 --> 00:01:51,664
Hello, have you been well, sir?

11
00:01:52,623 --> 00:01:54,959
If she's titled the Best Talent,

12
00:01:55,042 --> 00:01:57,128
she must be very talented.

13
00:01:59,839 --> 00:02:00,756
