I'll clean it.

27
00:03:18,793 --> 00:03:20,252
No, I'll do it, sir.

28
00:03:21,504 --> 00:03:22,713
I'll do it.

29
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,801
My apologies, sir.

30
00:03:26,884 --> 00:03:28,052
Allow me to do it.

31
00:03:28,135 --> 00:03:30,096
- Sa-rang, you may leave.
- No, ma'am.

32
00:03:30,179 --> 00:03:31,388
- I'll--
- Sa-rang?

33
00:03:44,276 --> 00:03:45,194
I'm sorry.

34
00:04:00,167 --> 00:04:01,210
- Mr. Gu.
- Yes.

35
00:04:02,837 --> 00:04:03,838
Goodness.

36
00:04:07,842 --> 00:04:09,218
- It's delicious.
- Is that so?

37
00:04:54,221 --> 00:04:56,599
EPISODE 13

38
00:04:57,224 --> 00:05:01,687
Seeing Won manage
the 100th-anniversary event made me think,

39
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:04,773
"This kid sure can put up an act."

40
00:05:04,857 --> 00:05:07,109
But it wasn't an act
by the looks of things today.

41
00:05:07,193 --> 00:05:09,737
He actually cares about his employees.

42
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:12,740
That's why I like him.

43
00:05:13,324 --> 00:05:15,367
He even takes care of people like her.

44
00:05:15,451 --> 00:05:18,245
He's different from
all the pretentious men out there.

45
00:05:19,622 --> 00:05:23,250
You're amazing for liking that about him.

46
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:29,006
Chairman Han and I
will arrange all the wedding preparations.

47
00:05:29,089 --> 00:05:30,174
Understood?

48
00:05:30,257 --> 00:05:31,634
Yes, Father.

49
00:05:33,594 --> 00:05:34,470
Won.

50
00:05:34,553 --> 00:05:35,596
What about you?

51
00:05:40,768 --> 00:05:41,727
I…

52
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,240
I…

53
00:05:55,699 --> 00:05:57,368
am in love with someone else.

54
00:06:02,957 --> 00:06:04,708
What were you thinking?

55
00:06:06,377 --> 00:06:07,336
I'm sorry.

56
00:06:08,087 --> 00:06:10,673
How did you join King the Land
with those skills?

57
00:06:10,756 --> 00:06:11,840
I'm sorry.

58
00:06:11,924 --> 00:06:14,885
I'll be the main server
and have Sa-rang assist me.

59
00:06:14,969 --> 00:06:17,388
How can I let her go back in
when she dropped a plate?

60
00:06:18,681 --> 00:06:20,891
I'll do the serving.
Stay on the second floor.

61
00:06:20,975 --> 00:06:23,852
Wouldn't the second floor
be too difficult for a new member?

62
00:06:23,936 --> 00:06:25,562
That's why you take charge there.

63
00:06:25,646 --> 00:06:27,439
- Ha-na.
- Yes, ma'am.

64
00:06:27,523 --> 00:06:29,817
Since when did King the Land
become so lax?

65
00:06:30,442 --> 00:06:32,361
It wasn't like that when I was there.

66
00:06:33,237 --> 00:06:34,780
It's the room at the very end.

67
00:06:34,863 --> 00:06:36,323
Let's not make any more mistakes.

68
00:06:37,866 --> 00:06:38,826
Yes, ma'am.

69
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:43,414
Gosh, I thought Won was just a kid.
He's all grown up now.

70
00:06:43,998 --> 00:06:45,666
He even has someone he loves.

71
00:06:46,375 --> 00:06:48,460
- Do you love her a lot?
- Yes.

72
00:06:48,544 --> 00:06:49,378
Of course.

73
00:06:49,461 --> 00:06:51,547
